    "name": "Car Manufacture: Prologue",
    "steam_appid": 1785980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/b390625f18682ea65c37d40e5bb66fe4.avif?t=1724760137\" width=610 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CAR MANUFACTURE - PROLOGUE</h2>Car Manufacture: Prologue 是一款关于建造和管理汽车工厂的游戏的简化版本。本游戏版本仅限于教程，在这里您将生产您的第一辆车，并学习生产和销售的基本机制。此外，还有一个挑战任务，您需要利用您的智慧来完成军用车辆的特殊订单。<br>您从20世纪初开始，只有几千美元，这些钱将用于建造您的第一家工厂。随着时间的推移，您将把一个简单的车间转变为高效的自动化工厂。在开发新车型和技术的同时，您还需要在不断增长的劳工权益运动面前管理您的员工。谨慎地建立您的品牌声誉并推广您的产品，以在竞争激烈的早期汽车工业市场中脱颖而出。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>创建一个完全定制的汽车工厂。<br></li><li>建立和优化装配线以实现高效生产。<br></li><li>管理多种类型的基于统计数据的员工。<br></li><li>推广产品并战略性地设定价格。<br></li><li>开发新车型。<br></li><li>提升您工厂的知名度以吸引更多客户。<br></li><li>参与行业活动并面对额外的挑战。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/054f865f14a673f9107aa43277487613.poster.avif?t=1724760137\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/054f865f14a673f9107aa43277487613.webm?t=1724760137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>建造最令人惊叹和最快的汽车！<br>20世纪初为我们带来了新的机会。展示出色领导者的素质，因为您将成为汽车工厂的负责人。汽车工业的未来将由您决定。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/981ade70fa7ca969febbca6da8d69f9b.poster.avif?t=1724760137\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/981ade70fa7ca969febbca6da8d69f9b.webm?t=1724760137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>扩展您的业务！<br>您将参与从头到尾的汽车制造过程。汽车一离开生产线就进行测试。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/29d853f9de69f8fefbe46e7c341614f1.poster.avif?t=1724760137\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/29d853f9de69f8fefbe46e7c341614f1.webm?t=1724760137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>雇佣最优秀的人才！<br>每辆您制造的汽车背后都有多多少少有经验的人。让工厂满负荷运转是您的责任。根据员工的技能分配任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/156199d7055e989190a6d2aba091825d.poster.avif?t=1724760137\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/156199d7055e989190a6d2aba091825d.webm?t=1724760137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>等待您的20世纪汽车工业！<br>生产线的发展是关键。先从单个站点开始，然后将其转变为更小、更高效的位置组。谁知道，也许将来您会成为一家完全独立的工厂，甚至生产最小的螺丝。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/086abe5f64f8033106380343604cea22.poster.avif?t=1724760137\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785980/extras/086abe5f64f8033106380343604cea22.webm?t=1724760137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>保持在顶端<br>在大企业中，很容易落后。研究新技术并雇用主管以确保最高速度的生产。",
